{"tid":1164104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法新社指美國將對華為的禁令延遲90天實施","createTime":"2019-05-21T00:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T01:43:08.000Z","uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"025872fc77a34ae5beaecd73a6245a0f6db1cb7a","tid":1164104,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:17:36.000Z","msg":"真定假？唔聽侵侵話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n07:18 法新社剛剛消息，美國官員周一決定，將對華為的禁令延遲90天實施，直到8月中旬才會生效，理由是，華為及其商業夥伴需要時間來升級軟件以及處理一些合同義務問題。(環球網)<br />\n<br />\n來自秒聞 ‧ 實時財經急報app<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mutemute.com/share.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mutemute.com%2Fshare.php&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=26ae59ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mutemute.com/share.php</a>"},{"pid":"b2ecd64aee61d5aff79a5a1729524661f9152867","tid":1164104,"uid":50386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:26:29.000Z","msg":"推遲實施並不意味着特朗普基於國家安全發佈的禁令被取消，而是為了讓華為及其合作伙伴「有時間」來維護支持當前全面運營的網絡和設備，包括軟件更新和補丁，以遵守2019年5月16日或者在這之前簽訂的具有法律約束力的合同和協議。」"},{"pid":"04b5015a1e8f0c0a6a22928f1f020d4436306bec","tid":1164104,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.litenews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_20180528_141051_processed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litenews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2FIMG_20180528_141051_processed.jpg&h=a94069d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0514/06DD711BEE5FCAF0D22C29FA4E8F753C5D9695FA_size103_w1080_h1076.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp0.ifengimg.com%2Fpmop%2F2018%2F0514%2F06DD711BEE5FCAF0D22C29FA4E8F753C5D9695FA_size103_w1080_h1076.jpeg&h=4b05a2a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<im